---
title: "Projects & Homelab"
layout: "layouts/page.njk"
description: "A showcase of my homelab infrastructure, open-source tools, and side projects I've built."
image: "/assets/images/jesus.webp"
sitemapPriority: 0.8
sitemapChangefreq: "monthly"
prose: true
---

<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
{%- for project in projects -%}
  <div class="card p-6">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
      <i class="fa-solid {{ project.icon }} text-2xl text-accent-primary"></i>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">{{ project.name }}</h3>
    </div>
    <p class="article-text mb-4">{{ project.description | safe }}</p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      {%- if project.link -%}
        <a href="{{ project.link }}" class="inline-block text-xs font-medium py-1 px-2.5 rounded-full border border-accent-primary/30 text-accent-primary hover:bg-accent-primary/10 transition-colors" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Source</a>
      {%- endif -%}
      {%- for tag in project.tags -%}
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium py-1 px-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent-primary/10 text-accent-primary">{{ tag }}</span>
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </div>
{%- endfor -%}
</div>

<h3>Infrastructure</h3>

<p class="article-text mb-6">
All services run on a Proxmox-based homelab behind <strong>OPNsense</strong> with nginx-proxy-manager handling reverse proxy and SSL termination oauth2-proxy for authentication. Docker nodes use Dockge for container management. The stack spans:
